WEBVTT

00:07.001 --> 00:09.161
An exchange would be made
in return for information.

00:09.201 --> 00:12.041
What do you have to give
that I could possibly want?

00:12.081 --> 00:13.801
Oslo have made Markus...
- He's our new governor.

00:13.841 --> 00:17.081
Are you all happy letting the town drunk
just wander around shooting a hunting rifle?

00:17.121 --> 00:19.641
He is not the town drunk!

00:19.681 --> 00:21.801
Hey, man. I got you, huh?
Whoa!

00:21.841 --> 00:23.361
You're in good hands.

00:23.401 --> 00:25.561
My husband has done this before.

00:25.601 --> 00:26.841
Do you want me, Boyd?

00:27.721 --> 00:30.001
The parasites, the wasps, the larvae,
they're dead and gone.

00:30.041 --> 00:33.241
A single specimen was preserved
in cryogenic suspension.

00:33.281 --> 00:35.081
I can't believe this.

00:35.121 --> 00:37.121
They didn't get on a plane,
they're still here.

00:37.161 --> 00:39.441
Lars?
- Morning, Mr Ulvinaune.

00:44.321 --> 00:47.841
<i>♪ The river did come to me ♪</i>

00:48.481 --> 00:51.561
<i>♪ Straight into my arms ♪</i>

00:53.281 --> 00:56.281
<i>♪ I tried to caress it ♪</i>

00:57.561 --> 01:01.521
<i>♪ But it ran through my fingers ♪</i>

01:03.881 --> 01:06.001
<i>♪ Water will keep running ♪</i>

01:06.041 --> 01:07.761
<i>♪ Rivers will turn ♪</i>

